data.meta_description:
65 likes, 3 comments - rememberingyugoslavia on May 4, 2021: "Time stood still 41 years ago today, when one Josip Broz Tito died, as it does now on the one 3D souvenir (other than books and rakija) I brought from my last trip to ex-Yugoslavia. No bones about it, the Insa wind-up alarm clock just tick-tocks too damn loud.
.
May the 4th be with you.
.
.
